<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D88781FF8AFFC1FF154BF4FB49FC55:8EAE604CFF8BFFC1FE4E4D77FD9CFC86" box="[460,530,809,835]" county="Wuming County" municipality="Mt. Daming" name="These" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" stateProvince="Guangxi">These</location>
specimens were examined by 
<bibRefCitation author="Song, D. X. &amp; Zhu, M. S. &amp; Chen, J." box="[891,1200,809,835]" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" refId="ref53995" refString="Song, D. X., Zhu, M. S. &amp; Chen, J. (1999) The Spiders of China. Hebei Science &amp; Technology Publishing House, Shijiazhuang, 640 pp." type="book" year="1999">Song, Zhu &amp; Chen (1999)</bibRefCitation>
who recorded them as 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D88781FF8AFFC1FF154BF4FB49FC55:8EAE604CFF8BFFC1FF3E4D0EFE94FCAF" box="[188,282,848,874]" county="Wuming County" municipality="Mt. Daming" name="Chinese" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" stateProvince="Guangxi">Chinese</location>
