<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D88781FF8AFFC1FF154BF4FB49FC55:8EAE604CFF8BFFC1FEA94D28FEF6FC55" box="[299,376,886,912]" county="Wuming County" municipality="Mt. Daming" name="Future" pageId="71" pageNumber="72" stateProvince="Guangxi">Future</location>
